Package: BiocDockerManager
Type: Package
Title: Manager for bioconductor docker images. 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nitesh", "Turaga", email = "nitesh.turaga@roswellpark.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Templating engine and manager for the bioconductor docker
    images on dockerhub. The package aims to update Dockerfiles uniformly
    and make it easy for the maintainers on the Bioconductor Team. The vignette
    also provides best practices for developers on how to inherit from these
    docker images and build their own.
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: 
    whisker
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
